reviewText: I think these guys should have more sex with men

This a compilation  of previous editions, nothing new covered, and not really the best features that could ahev been selected from.  I always wonder how they make these tapes and seldom have any ethnic men, American Indian men, or asian men.  Just your usual "white bread" American males.  I wish  they would  (1) make a 120 minute version for the same price (2) select a wider variety of men; and  (3) understand the concept of diversity/inclusion/.
